OL,3,C'Little privacy or dignity for
OL,4,Cpatients': An emergency department
OL,5,Cunder strain
OL,7,FWinter pressures continue to cause
OL,8,Flong waiting times at the Royal
OL,9,FVictoria Hospital (RVH) in Belfast.
OL,11,FUTV saw the strain on the facility
OL,12,Fduring exclusive access to the
OL,13,Femergency department.
OL,15,FHannah Rebecca Hanna is a Nurse-in-
OL,16,Fcharge at the emergency department in
OL,17,Fthe RVH.
