OL,3,C'Little privacy or dignity for
OL,4,Cpatients': An emergency department
OL,5,Cunder strain
OL,7,FShe said: "The worst things I have
OL,8,Fseen are these patients lying for
OL,9,Fdays, these elderly frail patients who
OL,10,Fare becoming more delirious, who
OL,11,Fpotentially have a risk of becoming
OL,12,Fmore unwell."
OL,14,F"There's patients in lots of non-
OL,15,Fclinical spaces because the department
OL,16,Fis overcapacity.
OL,18,F"Patients are having to be nursed in
OL,19,Fareas that they wouldn't normally be
OL,20,Fnursed in.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/11
