OL,3,C'Little privacy or dignity for
OL,4,Cpatients': An emergency department
OL,5,Cunder strain
OL,7,F"This is distressing for patients too
OL,8,Fas there's not a lot of privacy or a
OL,9,Flot of dignity," she said.
OL,11,FThe only space for some patients is on
OL,12,Fa corridor.
OL,14,F"It's difficult for the nurses as
OL,15,Fthey're having to move in between the
OL,16,Fpatients where there's not a lot of
OL,17,Froom to access them.
OL,19,F"Some days are slightly better, but
OL,20,Fmost of the time, this is the reality.
