OL,7,F"It's challenging, but they do take it
OL,8,Fin their stride and they do their very
OL,9,Fbest for the patients."
OL,11,FTeams continuously track patients
OL,12,Fbeing admitted and discharged across
OL,13,Fthe trust.
OL,15,FRed resus is the most intense corner
OL,16,Fof the emergency department and during
OL,17,Ffilming, all bays were full to
OL,18,Fcapacity.
