OL,3,C'Little privacy or dignity for
OL,4,Cpatients': An emergency department
OL,5,Cunder strain
OL,7,F"I'm right outside recess, so it's
OL,8,Fjust constant," she said.
OL,10,FRoisin Matthews said the situation is
OL,11,F"nerve wracking at times".
OL,13,F"You're sitting here and you don't
OL,14,Fknow who's going up and down past you."
OL,16,FMedical Director at the Belfast Trust,
OL,17,FChris Hagan said that winter pressures
OL,18,Fare "always difficult".
