OL,7,F"We are not unique in the fact that
OL,8,Funfortunately some patients have to
OL,9,Fspend some time in a corridor.
OL,11,F"That is not the care that we would
OL,12,Fwant to give them professionally," he
OL,13,Fadded.
OL,15,F"I think it's important that we
OL,16,Funderstand this isn't just the Royal,
OL,17,Fit's the Mater and the Children's
OL,18,FHospital.
