OL,3,C'Little privacy or dignity for
OL,4,Cpatients': An emergency department
OL,5,Cunder strain
OL,7,F"We run three busy emergency
OL,8,Fdepartments and we have focused on
OL,9,Ftrying to improve flow this year."
OL,11,FThe Belfast Trust has been working to
OL,12,Fkeep turnaround times to a minimum so
OL,13,Fthat patients aren't left for hours in
OL,14,Fcorridors.
OL,16,FMedical Director at the Northern
OL,17,FIreland Ambulance Service, Nigel
OL,18,FRuddell said any delay in responding
OL,19,Fto a patient "increases risk" to them.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/11
