OL,3,C'Little privacy or dignity for
OL,4,Cpatients': An emergency department
OL,5,Cunder strain
OL,7,F"We know that it can increase the
OL,8,Flength of stay that a patient
OL,9,Fexperiences when they're admitted to
OL,10,Fhospital if they're allowed to
OL,11,Fdeteriorate before they start getting
OL,12,Fdefinitive care.
OL,14,F"Certainly the risks are higher for
OL,15,Fanybody whose response is delayed or
OL,16,Fwhose admission is delayed," he said.
OL,18,FThe Community Discharge team works to
OL,19,Fsee which patients are well enough to
OL,20,Fleave hospital but need care in the
OL,21,Fcommunity.
