OL,3,C'Little privacy or dignity for
OL,4,Cpatients': An emergency department
OL,5,Cunder strain
OL,7,FUTV was told a lack of care homes
OL,8,Facross the system in Northern Ireland
OL,9,Fis a contributing factor to the strain
OL,10,Fon the system.
OL,12,FThe hospital discharge hub at the RVH
OL,13,Fwas under pressure to find community
OL,14,Fcare for patients who needed
OL,15,Fadditional support to leave.
OL,17,FOne of those patients was Betty
OL,18,FDonnelly who has terminal cancer.
